2003
drink means alcoholic drink
driver , in relation to a vehicle, includes the rider of the motorcycle or moped
or bicycle; and drive has a corresponding meaning
driver licence means a licence to drive that is issued or has effect under this
Act; and includes an endorsement on a driver licence
driver licence stop order means an order imposed under section 91E
