ted an infringement offence that may be enforced by a parking warden under
section 128E,—
(a) the user of the vehicle may be proceeded against for the alleged offence
under the Criminal Procedure Act 2011; or
(b) the parking warden may issue an infringement notice in respect of the
alleged offence.
