## 139AAC Annual quality assurance of automated infringement system

```
The Agency must ensure that an automated infringement system undergoes
annually a quality assurance process to ensure the ongoing capability of the
system—
(a) to verify the matters set out in section 139AAA(1); and
(b) to collect, hold, use, and disclose personal information in accordance
with the Privacy Act 2020.
