posed:
(eb) New Zealand’s international obligations concerning land transport
safety:
(f) the international circumstances in respect of land transport safety:
(g) such other matters as the Minister (in the case of ordinary rules) or the
Agency (in the case of emergency rules) considers appropriate in the
circumstances.
