**185 Vehicle importers must hold carbon dioxide accounts**

(1) Every vehicle importer who imports a Type A or Type B vehicle on or after
1 December 2022 must hold a carbon dioxide account with the Director.

(2) The account must contain the information and be operated in the manner
prescribed by the regulations.

Part 13 s 183 **Land Transport Act 1998**
