**186 Director must allocate unique numbers for carbon dioxide accounts**

```
The Director must, in accordance with the regulations, allocate a unique
account number to each carbon dioxide account when the account is opened.
Section 186: inserted, on 23 February 2022, by section 10 of the Land Transport (Clean Vehicles)
