**187 Carbon dioxide account information required for vehicle importation**

```
On and after 1 December 2022, no Type A or Type B vehicle may be certified
for entry under this Act, unless—
(a) the carbon dioxide account number of the vehicle importer has been
provided to the Director; and
(b) the carbon dioxide emissions of the vehicle have been recorded in the
vehicle importer’s carbon dioxide account.
