Section 270(8): repealed, on 1 January 2016, by section 14 of the Legislation (Confirmable Instru‐
ments) Amendment Act 2015 (2015 No 120).

```
Appointment
Heading: added, on 29 June 2009, by section 32(17) of the Land Transport Amendment Act 2009
(2009 No 17).
