**18 Exemptions granted under section 168D**

```
Class exemptions
```
(1) A class exemption is a disallowable instrument for the purposes of the Legis‐
lation Act 2012 and must be presented to the House of Representatives under
section 41 of that Act.

(2) As soon as practicable after granting a class exemption, the Director must—

```
