**19 Transport instruments**

(1) A transport instrument is a disallowable instrument, but not a legislative instru‐
ment, for the purposes of the Legislation Act 2012 and must be presented to the
House of Representatives under section 41 of that Act.

5 April 2025 **Land Transport Act 1998** Schedule 1


(2) The Agency, the Director, or the Secretary (as the case may be) must, as soon
as practicable after making, amending, or revoking a transport instrument,—
(a) notify the instrument, amendment, or revocation in the _Gazette_ (but need
not incorporate the text of the instrument, amendment, or revocation);
and
(b) ensure that a copy of the instrument, amendment, or revocation is—
(i) published on the Agency’s Internet site; and
(ii) available for purchase in hard copy at a reasonable charge.
